  "texts": [
    "Down sampling layers enable local translation invariance, minimize representation spatial size, and extract reduced-level feature maps.",
    "There are various models of encoder-decoder based on image segmentation in which U-Net (Liu et al. 2021a; Minaee et al. 2022; Ghosh et al. 2020) is the base model for image segmentation in biomedical analysis.",
    "Currently, there are limited studies that discuss the classification of encoder-decoder-based models and all variations of U-Net that are used to polyp segmentation in detail.",
    "In this literature study, the various models of U-Net are shown to be incredibly efficient and outperform the original U-Net.",
